                                        "title":  "Infinitiv mit zu",
                                        "text":  "Infinitive constructions with \u0027zu\u0027 are used after certain verbs, adjectives, and nouns. Special forms: um...zu (purpose), ohne...zu (without doing), anstatt...zu (instead of doing)."
