                                        "type":  "examples",
                                        "title":  "um ... zu (Zweck / Purpose)",
                                        "color":  "green",
                                        "items":  [
                                                      {
                                                          "de":  "Ich lerne Deutsch, um in Berlin zu arbeiten.",
                                                          "en":  "I learn German in order to work in Berlin."
